|rad3oui = |rad3_ant_conn = MHF4 |rad3mimostatus = Yes |rad3txchains = 4 |rad3rxchains = 4 |rad3sstreams = 4 |rad3stand = IEEE 802.11b/g/n/ax |rad3ax = 1148 |nqam3 = 1000 |rad3n = 600 |rad3g = 54 |rad3b = 11 |rad3freq = 2.4 |rad3correv = |rad3cap = }}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== :Supporting MU-MIMO and OFDMA technology, :built-in WTFast game accelerator and Adaptive QoS, :with AiProtection network security powered by Trend Micro *Web GUI: http://router.asus.com {{see also|ASUS GT-AX11000|ASUS RT-AX88U|ASUS RT-AX92U}} According to FCC documents, the RT-AX95U and the [[ASUS GT-AX11000|GT-AX11000]] (renamed from RT-AX11000) are identical. {{FCC ST|08/13/2018|indexme.}} ==Links of Interest== ===Forum threads=== *[https://www.snbforums.com/threads/and-so-it-begins-asus-announces-first-802-11ax-router.41020/page-4#post-382840 ''And So It Begins... Asus Announces First 802.11ax Router'' on '''SNB''' forums] *[https://www.snbforums.com/threads/asus-expands-11ax-lineup-and-sets-ship-date.47010/ ''ASUS Expands 11ax Lineup And Sets Ship Date'' on '''SNB''' forums] ==Notes== *'''Next-Gen WiFi Standard''' - 802.11ax WiFi standard for better efficiency and throughput *'''Ultrafast WiFi Speed''' - 11Gbps WiFi speed to handle even the busiest network with ease *'''Wider Usage and More Convenience''' - 8 antennas + 8 LAN ports to support more clients *'''Commercial-grade Security''' - AiProtection, powered by Trend Micro, blocks internet :security threats for all your connected smart devices *'''Better Partner with Mesh System''' - Compatible with ASUS AiMesh WiFi system :for seamless whole-home coverage
